General.Name: Helix Resources Ltd
General.Description: Helix Resources Limited engages in the mineral exploration activities in Australia. It explores for copper, gold, iron ore, nickel, cobalt, and other base metals. Its principal projects include the Collerina, the Rochford, and the Meryula projects. Helix Resources Limited was incorporated in 1985 and is based in Perth, Australia.
